strings.Value: "At least the local rabbits will rest easy, if we don't go hunting tonight. And we still have some rations."
"So no one's going to hunt tonight? Well, at least that's good for some rabbit or deer, who will live to see another dawn."
"I pity the rabbits, of course, but I'd prefer one or two hop into our stew pot. A fresh meal is always healthier."
"Damn it, cleric. Hunting is fun and meat is tasty. But you're just a rabbit lover who likes chewing ration packs!"
"Rabbits are so cute! But so tasty too! â€” I can't tell which one's more important."
"Ha. You put an animal higher than yourself. You think almost as little of yourself as I do..."
"You care so much for those who are unable to protect themselves! It's a shame your brothers in faith didn't show me the same mercy."
